{include file="header.tpl"}
<div id="container">
	<div class="method">
		<header id="header">
			<h1>How does it work?</h1>
		</header>
		<section>
			<header>
				<h1>Before your event</h1>
			</header>
			<aside class="method-invite">
				<header>
					<h1>Send invites</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Easily send invites to all your friends and contacts.</p>
			</aside>
			<aside class="method-rsvp">
				<header>
					<h1>Collect RSVPs</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Guests RSVP using options based on their actual behavior.</p>
			</aside>
			<aside class="method-text">
				<header>
					<h1>Send last minute texts</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Be only a text message away from your guests so they can receive timely updates.</p>
			</aside>
		</section>
		<section>
			<header>
				<h1>During your event</h1>
			</header>
			<aside class="method-mobile">
				<header>
					<h1>Mobile check in</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Check off attendees using our app to improve your trueRSVP for your next event.</p>
			</aside>
			<aside class="method-qr">
				<header>
					<h1>QR Check in</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Easily scan all your attendees into your event using QR codes.</p>
			</aside>
			<aside class="method-feed">
				<header>
					<h1>Enjoy your live feed</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Have a personalized event page that gathers tweets and photos your guests have posted.</p>
			</aside>
		</section>
		<section>
			<header>
				<h1>After your event</h1>
			</header>
			<aside class="method-reputation">
				<header>
					<h1>Guests' reputation</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Whether or not each guest actually showed up to your event affects their reliability rating. See who flaked on you and who is reliable!</p>
			</aside>
			<aside class="method-email">
				<header>
					<h1>Follow up on your guests</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Send follow up e-mails and texts to get feedback and more about your event.</p>
			</aside>
			<aside class="method-truersvp">
				<header>
					<h1>Your next event gets better!</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Your trueRSVP is more accurate and your guests are more committed if you use our system!</p>
			</aside>
		</section>
	</div>
</div>
